Sprite creation and use for python

https://github.com/drekels/python-sprite

This repo contains the sprite python package, which is used for arranging 
related images into atlases.  

Features:
* Create image atlas with meta file from a set of images
* Create and read animation meta files


Dependencies
------------

See requirements.txt


Usage
-----

pip install --upgrade git+https://github.com/drekels/python-sprite.git@STABLE


Known Issues
------------

No known issues (mostly due to ignorance)


